PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q5513 wdt:P2046 ?areaBaikal .
  wd:Q5525 wdt:P2046 ?areaGreatBear .
  FILTER ( ?areaBaikal > ?areaGreatBear )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
SELECT ?mountain ?mountainLabel ?elevation_m WHERE {
  ?mountain wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q8502 .
  ?mountain wdt:P17 wd:Q408 .
  ?mountain p:P2044 ?eStmt .
  ?eStmt psv:P2044 ?vnode .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?vnode wikibase:quantityNormalized ?norm .
    ?norm wikibase:quantityAmount ?normAmount .
    ?norm wikibase:quantityUnit wd:Q11573 .
  }
  OPTIONAL {
    ?vnode wikibase:quantityAmount ?amount .
    ?vnode wikibase:quantityUnit wd:Q11573 .
  }
  BIND( xsd:decimal ( COALESCE ( ?normAmount , ?amount ) ) AS ?elevation_m ) OPTIONAL {
    ?mountain rdfs:label ?mountainLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?mountainLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?elevation_m )
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?cave ) AS ?caveCount ) ?countryLabel WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P17 ?country .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
GROUP BY ?country ?countryLabel
HAVING ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?cave ) > 10 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?caveCount )

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?city ?cityLabel ( MAX( ?pop ) AS ?population ) WHERE {
  ?city wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q515 .
  ?city wdt:P131 + wd:Q1408 .
  ?city wdt:P1082 ?pop .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?city rdfs:label ?cityLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?cityLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
GROUP BY ?city ?cityLabel
HAVING ( MAX( ?pop ) > 100000 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?population )
